description:
Centrum for Women 50+ multivitamin and minerals are complete from A to Zinc and support vitality, post-menopausal health, immunity and bone health

Centrum for Women 50+ is a daily multivitamin specifically designed for women aged 50 and over, to support energy, post-menopausal health, healthy bones and healthy immune function. Each tablet contains multiple vitamins to help fill nutritional gaps.

Increased levels of iron, calcium and vitamin D* to support post menopausal health

Increased levels* of calcium and vitamin D to maintain healthy bones. *Compared to Centrum Advance 50+

With key antioxidants such as vitamins A, C & E, betacarotene, selenium and zinc to support healthy immune function

With B vitamins and folic acid to support vitality
name: Centrum Women 50+ Daily Multivitamin Supplements 60 Pack
